            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once hot, add most of the <strong>sliced red onion</strong> (save the rest for garnish!) with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 3-4 min or until softened</p><p>Once softened, add the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>garlic</strong> with the <strong>ground coriander</strong>, <strong>dried chilli flakes </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and the <strong>remaining cumin</strong> and <strong>smoked paprika</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and cook for 1-2 min or until fragrant</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1650988649451-x200.jpg",
