            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, dissolve the <strong>chicken stock mix </strong>and <strong>tomato paste</strong> in 400ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[700ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong> with the <strong>soy sauce</strong> – this is your <strong>tomato stock</strong></p><p>Drain and rinse the <strong>black beans</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1650988654721-x200.jpg",
