      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Mexican-style chicken & black bean pilaf </strong>and sprinkle over the <strong>grated cheese</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>remaining sliced red onion </strong>and season with a crack of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
